| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1881 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d123eab1-b3e1-5a19-aff7-e3f7bdd62d65"
